title: Below Deck Med Trailer Breakdown!
description:
The new Below Deck Mediterranean trailer dropped recently, and we're here to break it down shot by shot, frame by frame. Come join us as we make flash impressions of the new cast and season!

Watch the trailer along with us using Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/68418243
